reviewText: It is a rare eye opener seminar about real spiritual awakening that leads to the evolution of the human body turning into light.

AMAZING.. I was so excited when I was first introduced to Mitchell Earl Gibson MD and his teachings. With his background, education, and demonstrations on Youtube, his credibility is above reproach. He's got a lot more to offer on his site [...]. I don't know why he doesn't offer it all through Amazon. Anyway, I just can't praise his work enough. It can't be easy, being one of the for fore fathers of higher level thinking and having those real life physical experiences, about things in our hearts we know exist, we just can't find the words to explain..he even does demonstrations on youtube that are simply AMAZING.. Love and Light..
In medical terms, it is known as hallucination.
OMG people!  Go back to the Bible and get The Truth!  Don't open yourself to this dark side that is disguised.....
